{"tid":1499304,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"抗爭核彈級工具，亦都係最影響世界觀嘅方法","createTime":"2019-08-23T16:13:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T17:14:40.000Z","uid":135762,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1beda78cea196469f1a04e3db78ec1d8b2d69b34","tid":1499304,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:13:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">National Anthem<br />\n<br />\nof<br />\n<br />\nUnited State of America</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6pugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=f8068f87\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">O say can you see by the dawn's early light,<br />\n<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed <br />\n<br />\nat the twilight's last gleaming,<br />\n<br />\nWhose broad stripes and bright stars <br />\n<br />\nthrough the perilous fight<br />\n<br />\nO'er the ramparts we watched, <br />\n<br />\nwere so gallantly streaming?<br />\n<br />\nAnd the rockets' red glare, <br />\n<br />\nthe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<br />\nGave proof through the night that <br />\n<br />\nour flag was still there;<br />\n<br />\nO say does that star-spangled banner yet wave,<br />\n<br />\nO'er the land of the free <br />\n<br />\nand the home of the brave?<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n身為香港人 身份比較特殊<br />\n由細到大其實對國家呢個概念<br />\n係極度模糊<br />\n特別係以前小學個個禮拜都要奏國歌<br />\n依家諗返起真係好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我哋淨係知道<br />\n香港回歸後<br />\n大陸淨係識得搞我哋呢隻金蛋<br />\n為求目的不擇手段  取得所有利益<br />\n所有基建其實英治時期已經好完善<br />\n回歸後幾乎所有嘅設施唔係為香港人而做<br />\n反而大白象多的是<br />\n吸乾我哋香港人血汗錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家仲想搞鳩我哋嘅外匯儲備<br />\n攞完錢仲要送我哋返大陸坐監?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傻的嗎？<br />\n高技術高/生產力奴隸？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國家國歌對我嚟講完全不是一回事<br />\n可有可無<br />\n歌詞內容仲要同執政/人民精神完全相違背<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係美國甚至乎其他高級歐洲國家<br />\n國歌對佢哋係極神聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟要係一個咩政權<br />\n先要令一個其他國家嘅人民<br />\n唱佢哋嘅國歌尋求幫助/表達不滿<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋下次集會<br />\n要高舉美國國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n合唱美國國歌<br />\n上次淨係一個巴打唱已經咁有感染力<br />\n如果我哋幾千人一齊唱呢？<br />\n已經唔使叫你十幾萬人一齊開口<br />\n幾千人啫  求下你地啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋<br />\n如果喺合唱時候放催淚彈<br />\n嘿嘿 黑警真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行為係極度得罪美國<br />\n無論係對美國公民<br />\n定係係愛國者<br />\n都係一種侮辱<br />\n特別係軍人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望我哋可以喚醒更多美國公民<br />\n支持我哋追求民主自由<br />\n令美國國會更多議員發聲 對中共強烈施壓<br />\n我相信如果更美國人知道我哋係咁<br />\n一定會有一群民眾出嚟遊行支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我相信我哋會贏</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/byAbhpG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbyAbhpG.jpg&h=b7d911f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Give Me Democracy<br />\nOr<br />\nGive Me Death</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢排Reddit 日日都有有關香港/反送中<br />\n希望每日都可以更爆更火<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n讓全世界更認識中呢個大魔頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n同我背撚左1分30秒嘅歌詞佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5906fd9515f448f354d5cc57f7b8cad6e195e00","tid":1499304,"uid":135762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:15:36.000Z","msg":"對唔住  係United State<span style=\"color: red;\">s</span>呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d41ea38841d2fd102825ca07a8b1db3c265f31c","tid":1499304,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:18:53.000Z","msg":"好kiu口<br />\n不過會試<br />\nSpotify已download"},{"pid":"507bf57e4f7e89716b59f45491df43be6ee145f0","tid":1499304,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:21:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c207d5e7c41f29a18cb4b0a73bf01586ce72c07a","tid":1499304,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ccec18e9d0c436177c098b3dbc70f228e746484f","tid":1499304,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16528dcee41017a3e69f242ffdf47e061343386","tid":1499304,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:26:29.000Z","msg":"背緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一嚟激撚死共產黨<br />\n二嚟首歌真係好熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n噢，說吧！你可看見，從晨曦的曙光中，<br />\n讓我們對着陰暮僅餘一道光自豪地歡呼，<br />\n激戰過後，那寛闊的條紋和明亮的星星，<br />\n依然英勇飄揚，在我軍堡壘上？<br />\n火箭的紅色閃焰，半空的爆炸，<br />\n皆見證了，國旗徹夜安好無缺；<br />\n噢，說吧，星條旗仍高高飄揚在<br />\n這自由國土，勇者的家園之上？"},{"pid":"738a90e80bd502a64b7e97c05dd30bb4b139088a","tid":1499304,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"10月1號 美國旗海賀国慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e9a9c6cad812688b1a330196447931e7bc1c9a","tid":1499304,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"738a90e80bd502a64b7e97c05dd30bb4b139088a","tid":1499304,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:26:50.000Z","msg":"10月1號 美國旗海賀国慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:28:49.000Z","msg":"10月1號<br />\n<br />\n國慶日<br />\n<br />\n我哋唱國歌慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8898e8fc7414c9223180c26448a1740a5429b2b","tid":1499304,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:30:26.000Z","msg":"本來諗住818唱 可惜落雨"},{"pid":"30877a31e212b313990a96f5200983a849ccb754","tid":1499304,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:30:39.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n【突發文宣計劃第二期！】"},{"pid":"b336391135a806d86e10234248e618bbef8677dc","tid":1499304,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:34:33.000Z","msg":"其實中國國歌都係好勵志<br />\n<br />\n可惜比支那搞臭哂<br />\n<br />\n個作者仲比支那批鬥死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e7e70901d309228b66d33037d5d4ee92b75094","tid":1499304,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b336391135a806d86e10234248e618bbef8677dc","tid":1499304,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:34:33.000Z","msg":"其實中國國歌都係好勵志<br />\n<br />\n可惜比支那搞臭哂<br />\n<br />\n個作者仲比支那批鬥死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:37:10.000Z","msg":"第一句已經錯撚晒<br />\n根本全部就係奴隸"},{"pid":"38836ba2583c716026f4b9f31fe1c80ce7802fd0","tid":1499304,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24e7e70901d309228b66d33037d5d4ee92b75094","tid":1499304,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b336391135a806d86e10234248e618bbef8677dc","tid":1499304,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:34:33.000Z","msg":"其實中國國歌都係好勵志<br />\n<br />\n可惜比支那搞臭哂<br />\n<br />\n個作者仲比支那批鬥死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:37:10.000Z","msg":"第一句已經錯撚晒<br />\n根本全部就係奴隸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:14:40.000Z","msg":"佢呼喚不願做奴隸的人起來啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想繼續做奴隸嘅可以自生自滅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDiu 愈諗愈覺得香港到了最危險的時刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}